verbose_text: Although this method is not strictly quantitative, in cells, which were high for Hes1 (XREF_FIG D and 3E, arrows), miR-9-2 expression was relatively weak, while cells expressing low amounts of Hes1 had increased levels of miR-9-2 transcription (XREF_FIG D and 3E, representative cells shown by arrowheads).
